user_location: of Buskers Authentic Irish Pub and Restaurant Rhode Island
review_blob: This is a sub par beer that has been brewed by contract for the Newport Restaurant Group. They have replaced it with a from Grey Sail brewed in conjunction with their beverage manager. The only place you can now get this beer is Trio in Narragansett which isnt even open full time at this time of year. Id rather have a Blue Moon.
